snippet.title: Fate/Grand Order part 1267: [LIVE] Servant showcase w/ @Misaki Nobunaga Ch. Amber Glow
snippet.description:
Time for the annual look at my Servant collection! This time I'm doing it live, and I've brought along a special guest; VTuber and good friend Misaki Nobunaga!

Misaki's channel: https://www.youtube.com/c/MisakiNobunagaChAmberGlow

Full game playthrough: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLBC8w17FA1cv9oe63cGhYEhlaqyQxAl6v
Individual playlists by Singularity/event: https://www.youtube.com/user/pokedude9OO/playlists?view=50&sort=dd&shelf_id=6

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/pokedude900
Ko-fi: https://ko-fi.com/pokedude900
